Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:50.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}保坂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.02,0:01:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然真是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们会去春香家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋啊  今天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  保坂学长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去的人是我  速水学姐和淳子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人请您去…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是自然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我和南春香甚至还没说过话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有理由会请我去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好这人至少还能想明白这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还真是伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想得到邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须先做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么样和她搭话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.39,0:02:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离放学没多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动必须要有计划性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:02:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您试图在放学前成为春香的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水学姐  有点儿事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要告诉那男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我们要去春香家？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人现在也想去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他盯上春香了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么有趣的事你怎么不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫春香来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水学姐不能指望了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能由我来保护春香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:03:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她远离那恶棍的魔爪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…保坂学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保坂的模拟场景\N雨中邂逅篇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样南春香就会不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时我就露出醉人的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就很完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水学姐  什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:47.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保坂的模拟场景\N公园的雪中约会篇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样南春香就会羞得低下头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时我就将她搂入怀中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题就是之后要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题在于…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  您是为了和她交朋友才有这模拟场景的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我爱你」和「我喜欢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一句比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:38.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：敬体句和简体句的差别而已）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？有什么不同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫「有什么不同」  当然有很大不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不一样吧
